{
  "1118965": "fast-xml-builder attribute quote bypass (GHSA-5wm8-gmm8-39j9) via @aws-sdk/xml-builder->fast-xml-parser->fast-xml-builder@1.1.5. Fix is in fast-xml-builder@1.1.7+ but @aws-sdk/xml-builder (latest) has not yet updated to fast-xml-parser@5.7.3. Attack vector requires controlling XML attribute values passed to the builder; the AWS SDK controls these inputs internally. Remove once AWS SDK updates its fast-xml-parser dependency.",
